text: Motion
Motion
Motion
──Good morning, Producer!
Hey, good morning Natsuha.
You're quite early──
Did I happen to be late?

No, there's still plenty of time.
I just came early and waited.
I see...

Did you hurry here by any chance?
You seem a little out of breath.

No, it's not that.
I was warming up until just now.

I went for a run around the camp area.
The varying terrain provided a good workout.

Oh, impressive as always, Natsuha.
You're always so dedicated.

...It's nothing like that.
I actually planned to wake up earlier this morning...
...But, well, I ended up oversleeping a bit...
Haha, well, everyone has those days.

...Yeah, you're right. It's more important
to move forward than to regret the past.

...Yeah, I've decided! I'll increase the amount
of self-practice to make up for oversleeping.

...We still have some time left.
I'm going to do some stretching, Producer.
Sure, go ahead.

...Haha.
You really are Natsuha after all.
